    "entry": "ApexSigma Accumulated Historical Knowledge and Experience Dataset",
    "details": "This record synthesizes the operational status, critical decisions, and foundational knowledge of the ApexSigma and DevEnviro multi-agent software ecosystems. It serves as the single source of truth, documenting successes, failures, and architectural principles for future learning and development.",
